<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>NutriCompare | Сравнение питательных веществ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<main>
    <div class="app-container">
        <header class="app-header">
            <h1>🍏 NutriCompare</h1>
            <p>Сравнение питательных веществ в свежих фруктах и овощах</p>
        </header>

        <div class="search-box">
            <input type="text" id="food-search" placeholder="Search for a raw fruit/vegetable..." list="food-suggestions" />
            <datalist id="food-suggestions"></datalist>
        </div>

        <div id="selected-foods" class="selected-foods"></div>

        <div class="nutrient-filters">
            <h3>Фильтры нутриентов</h3>
            <div class="filter-controls">
                <input type="text" id="filter-search" placeholder="Поиск нутриентов...">
                <button id="select-all">Выбрать все</button>
                <button id="deselect-all">Снять все</button>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-checkboxes" id="nutrient-checkboxes"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="visualization-controls">
            <button id="toggle-visualization" class="active">Проанализировать на одном графике</button>
            <button id="show-pie-charts">Визуализировать каждый отдельно</button>
        </div>

        <div id="bar-chart-container" class="chart-container">
            <canvas id="nutrient-chart"></canvas>
        </div>

        <div id="pie-charts-container" class="pie-charts-container"></div>
    </div>
</main>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
<script src="~/js/site.js"></script>
</body>
</html>